    <p class="font-body-ui text-on-surface leading-relaxed">Calculate the net flux of the vector field <span class="math-formula font-body-math text-lg px-1 text-secondary font-semibold">F(x, y, z) = xi + yj + zk</span> across the unit sphere.</p>
